    </div>

    <div class="row">
        
        <div id="homeContentRight">
<p>Open Country Dairy represents the very best of the New Zealand Dairy industry. <span>Built on this solid foundation, Open Country Dairy has become the second largest global exporter of </span><span style="line-height: 1.2;">premium </span><span style="line-height: 1.2;">Whole Milk Powders. </span><span style="line-height: 1.2;">Our dairy products are valued for their quality around the world by producers of fine food and beverages. </span>We share our passion for dairying with our farmers and this close working relationship provides a quality milk supply that we process into Milk Powders, Milk Proteins, Milk Fats and Cheeses ready for our global customers. Our strong supplier network is the key to our global dairying success - <span style="line-height: 1.2;">The Best In Dairy. </span></p>
